==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la}} ''[[infero|inferō]]''.

===Pronunciation===
* {{audio|en-us-infer.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb|infer|r|ing}}

# {{transitive}} To [[surmise]] or [[reason]] from [[circumstance]].
# {{transitive}} To [[conclude]] by [[reason]]ing or [[deduction]], as from [[premise]]s or [[evidence]].
# {{intransitive}} To draw a conclusion (by [[reason]]ing).
# {{transitive|nonstandard|proscribed}} To [[imply]]: to have as a [[necessary]] [[consequence]].

====Synonyms====
* [[assume]], [[conclude]], [[deduce]]

